name: PURPLE REIGN
description:
my family had left me and after nearing homelessness 
i was able to stay on a relatives couch 
i was able to buy a phone and went for a night stroll @ the park

the sky was so purple, birds were flying everywhere and it started raining as i got there

this was the 1st photo i took

shot in texas, usa on iphone
